Summary: Saw what looked like commercial airliner but where jet engines shout be was huge spotlighted aircraft was only 20 feet above trees could see details besides the huge lighted what struck me as odd was no sound only sound heard was air displacement
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Graysville
There were no other sightings in Graysville on or around April 21st 2007
divs: Sighting DetailsWas laying in driveway just looking at stars like I like to do often when large plane like object flew over me. Where jet engines should have been were large spotlights. 4-5 ft across. Two total. Reminded me of headlights on a vw bug. The aircraft as large as it was flew only yards above the trees. The craft made no sound at all. After it passed I could hear only the sound of the air being displaced. Kinda like a wind. I don't know what it was some sort of secret propulsion system being used on regular cargo type pane or what. Don't think it was alien craft but maybe a way to test alien propulsion system in disguise. Any it was Unidentified an it was a flying object for sure
